fields.name: youthgroup
fields.question: First we need 2 know, are you part of any group? If yes, send us the NAME o+f the group. If no, text NO and just wait for the next set of instructions.

fields.name: district

fields.name: contactname
fields.question: Best responses may be shared!Send us your name,or if you prefer a nickname so we can give u recognition for good replies by sharing them in the media!
